Directed by Sri Saripalli

Written by Sri Saripalli

Star Kartikeya Gummakonda (Vikram). Tanya S Ravichandran (Kanthi (as Tanya)). Sudhakar Komakula (Govind Narayana). Sai Kumar (Chakravarthy). Pasupathy (Guru Narayana). Tanikella Bharani (Mahendra). Harshavardhan (Muddu Krishna). Surya (Suryam). Dayanand Reddy (Veerabhadram)

Language Telugu

Producers 88 Rama Reddy

Production Sree Chitra Movie Makers
